{"metadata":{"externalID":"s:12UltraliteSDK12ScrollLayoutC6ActionO6scrollyA2EmF","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"scroll","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"UltraliteSDK"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Case","title":"ScrollLayout.Action.scroll","symbolKind":"case"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK","doc:\/\/UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout","doc:\/\/UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/Action"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/Action\/scroll"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"scroll"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout\/action\/scroll"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/ScrollLayout/Action":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/Action","title":"ScrollLayout.Action","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Action","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Action"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Actions that can be used on a .scroll layout"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout\/action"},"doc://UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/ScrollLayout/Action/scroll":{"fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"scroll"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/Action\/scroll","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout\/action\/scroll","title":"ScrollLayout.Action.scroll","kind":"symbol"},"doc://UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"UltraliteSDK","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK","abstract":[{"text":"Use this SDK to easily send text and images to your Vuxix smart glasses.","type":"text"}]},"doc://UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/ScrollLayout":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ScrollLayout","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"When Ultralite.requestControl with a .scroll layout type .. this is the class you interate with to draw scrolling text to the screen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Once the layout is .scrolled you must send one configure message to tell the layout how to setup.  It will setup the slice height and how many slices are visible.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There are two supported modes: autoScroll on\/off"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When autoScroll is true, the slices are automatically scrolled.  Subscribe to the delgate and listen for the scrolled callback, when you get it send another slice of text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When autoScroll is false, you can drive the slices and how they look on the screen.  You can send all the slices at once or send one at a time and animate it onto the screen at the current time."}],"title":"ScrollLayout","identifier":"doc:\/\/UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ScrollLayout"}]}}}